@startuml
title Browse/Join Rooms

' ============== ACTORS & COMPONENTS ==============
actor "User" as User
participant "Controller/Input Manager" as Ctrl
participant "HUD" as HUD
participant "Network Manager" as Net
participant "Voice Chat" as Voice

' ============== TRIGGER ==============
User ->> Ctrl : Opens Join Room
Ctrl ->> HUD : Open "Join a Room"

' ============== LISTING ==============
HUD ->> Net : Poll live public rooms
Net --> HUD : Live room list

HUD --> User : Show: live public room list\n+ "Enter Code" input\n+ "Create Room" button

User ->> Ctrl : Selects option

' ============== FLOW A: Public Room from list ============
alt Flow A — Join public room (from list)
  User ->> Ctrl : Taps a room from list
  Ctrl ->> HUD : Join selected room
  HUD ->> Net : Join room
  Net --> HUD : Status: Connecting…

  Net ->> Net : Start client
  Net --> HUD : Connected

  HUD ->> Voice : Join voice channel
  Voice --> User : Voice/chat active

' ============== FLOW B: Join via Code ============
else Flow B — Join via room code
  User ->> Ctrl : Enters room code
  Ctrl ->> HUD : Submit join code
  HUD ->> Net : Join room by code

  alt Code valid / room found
    Net ->> Net : Set up relay
    Net ->> Net : Start client
    Net --> HUD : Connected

    HUD ->> Voice : Join voice channel
    Voice --> User : Voice/chat active

  else Code invalid / room not found
    Net --> HUD : Room not found
    HUD --> User : Show error: "Room not found.\nPlease try a new code."
  end

' ============== FLOW C: Create Room ============
else Flow C — Create room
  User ->> Ctrl : Taps "Create Room"
  Ctrl ->> HUD : Navigate to Create Room
  HUD --> User : [See: Create Room use case]

end

@enduml
